'''NGC 2058'''（或記作'''ESO 56-SC173'''）是位於[[山案座|山案座]]的[[疏散星团|疏散星团]]，收錄於原版[[NGC天體表|天體新總表]]（{{lang|en|NGC}}），屬於[[大麥哲倫星系|大麥哲倫星系]]。1982年，科學家利用光電[[光度測定_(天文學)|測光術]]和照相測光術<!--https://terms.naer.edu.tw/ -->，繪出NGC 2058和[[NGC_2065|NGC 2065]]的[[星系顏色-星等圖|顏色-星等圖]]，從而估計兩者的年齡為一億二千萬年。<ref>{{cite journal|first = P. J.|last = Flower|url = https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1982PASP...94..894F/abstract|title = Color-magnitude diagrams and ages of two young Magellanic Cloud clusters|doi = 10.1086/131081|journal = Publications of the Astronomical Society of the Pacific|date = 1982-12|volume = 94|issue = 562|pages = 894–900|access-date = 2022-03-06|archive-date = 2021-04-26|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210426122752/https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1982PASP...94..894F/abstract}}</ref>

